Itu mobil polisi!

207
00:13:34.705 --> 00:13:36.405
Hei, di sana.

208
00:13:36.405 --> 00:13:38.605
Kami tidak menyelinap masuk secara gratis!

209
00:13:40.005 --> 00:13:44.105
Bukankah kau detektif SMA itu?

210
00:13:44.105 --> 00:13:45.905
Aku Shinichi Kudo.

